description: The first of our 2017 boats are here! Take a look at the actual line of performance Tritoons with up to 300hp, and Chaparral sport boats and wake surf boats with towers! Boating without owning! What a great alternative to boat ownership at a fraction of the cost. The main problem with boating for most busy families is that they don't have the time or the inclination to deal with boat ownership. As a member of the Carefree Boat Club, you have unlimited usage of a new fleet of boats on South Holston, Boone, and Watauga Lakes, as well as nearly 50 other locations across the country. The club boasts a wide variety of pontoon and water sport boats, and we take care of storage, maintenance, cleaning, and insurance. We also offer on the water education and training for our members. You may be a past boat owner or someone who might not consider buying a boat but still wants to experience the freedom and thrill that comes with boating. Schedule a tour today at any of our locations. Feel free to give us a call, email, or visit our website at www.carefreeboats.com/watauga. Boating without the hassle of owning...it's about time!
title: Boating without the hassles of owning! Carefree Boat Club
